Plot basic phyloseq cladogram

library(phyloseq)
# plot(ps_tree)

Plot lefse LDA heatmap

library(microbiomeMarker)
data(kostic_crc)

ps <- kostic_crc
phy <- phyloseq::subset_taxa(
    ps,
    Phylum %in% c("Firmicutes")
)
mm_lefse <- run_lefse(
    phy,
    wilcoxon_cutoff = 0.01,
    group = "DIAGNOSIS",
    kw_cutoff = 0.01,
    multigrp_strat = TRUE,
    lda_cutoff = 1
)
plot_heatmap(mm_lefse, group = "DIAGNOSIS")
## Warning in transform_log10(otu): OTU table contains zeroes. Using log10(1 + x)
## instead.

Plot lefse LDA cladogram

data(kostic_crc)
kostic_crc_small <- phyloseq::subset_taxa(
    kostic_crc,
    Phylum %in% c("Firmicutes")
)
mm_lefse <- run_lefse(
    kostic_crc_small,
    wilcoxon_cutoff = 0.01,
    group = "DIAGNOSIS",
    kw_cutoff = 0.01,
    multigrp_strat = TRUE,
    lda_cutoff = 4
)
plot_cladogram(mm_lefse, color = c("darkgreen", "red"))
